examples.en: I requested a taxi for 8 o'clock.
Prompt payment is requested.
Her lawyer requested a change of venue.
He requested a posting to China.
Passengers are requested to examine their tickets and change before leaving.
Visitors are requested not to walk on the grass.
He requested the immediate dispatch of supplies.
The defense requested leniency in light of their client's lack of a prior criminal record.
Your full cooperation is requested.
She requested an extra bed in her room.
He requested a window seat for the flight.
I requested information from the secretary.
She requested a six-month deferment on her loan.
I requested that she type the entire manuscript.
Gentlemen are requested to wear a jacket and tie.
Your presence is requested at the club meeting on Friday.
All club members are requested to attend the annual meeting.
Having touched the piano, he was requested to sing. (J. W. Burgon)
Robert requested a bill of particulars for the care he received in the hospital.
The Police Committee requested a grant from the Government to cover the extra expense.
The developer requested a variance to build a shopping center on the east side of town.
Exasperated, the army surgeon requested a helpmeet who wouldn't faint at the sight of blood.
